<donors class="MCRMetaLangText" heritable="false" notinherit="false"><donor xml:lang="en" inherited="0" form="plain">Additiones 1 and 2 mention ʾAmätä ʾIyäsus as the donor.&#13;
Several names are written in a secondary hand in the supplication formulas: Gäbrä Mäsqäl (e.g., fols. 15rb, 19vb, 25vb, 37ra, 39va), ʾAmätä ʾIyäsus (e.g., fols. 14va, 16vb, 30ra), ʾAmätä Maryam (e.g., fols. 16va, 23rb, 30rb) and Wälättä Haymanot (e.g., fols. 17va, 23ra, 40vb, 47vb).</donor>
</donors>
